# results

**Instance Property**

The most recently received search completions.

## Declaration

```swift
var results: [MKLocalSearchCompletion] { get }
```

## Discussion

This property is `nil` initially. After a successful query, the search completer sets this property to the array of [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MKLocalSearchCompletion] objects that the query returns. Each new successful query replaces the previous value of this property.
